{"tid":1023556,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股神「軍師」芒格：續看好比亞迪前景","createTime":"2019-02-16T00:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T06:03:39.000Z","uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"61a2162407d93ed0d44eeec9f85142d07360791f","tid":1023556,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:48:08.000Z","msg":"「股神」巴菲特多年來的投資夥伴及「軍師」、巴郡副主席芒格(Charlie Munger)出席Daily Journal周年股東大會時表示，比亞迪(01211)未來在電動車及單軌鐵路領域發展潛力巨大，對於巴郡而言是一項出色的投資。<br />\n<br />\n他續提到，中國一直有許多投資機會，但很多美國人錯過了。<br />\n<br />\n巴郡去年第三季增持了蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)的股票，芒格重申對於Apple業務經營感到正面，但拒絕置評巴郡在Apple的持股，並坦言還不清楚如果解釋蘋果公司近日股價波動。另外，在下半年購入了更多銀行和保險公司的股票，使公司成為美國五大銀行中4家的主要股東。<br />\n<br />\n芒格又表示，選擇何時退出一項投資是相當困難的決定，而他更傾向不退出投資項目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Ip1Mdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ip1Mdk&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qpqf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=eb780c35\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Ip1Mdk</a>"},{"pid":"b96884f0b4bf200cde25d274dc3e7964ed0d3609","tid":1023556,"uid":53247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:49:23.000Z","msg":"一直等緊佢跌"},{"pid":"9fac06b53b636bdb55c98aeb5b99450cec649ab6","tid":1023556,"uid":123559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:20:54.000Z","msg":"比亞迪 we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08406fb029090d1b09bc76f6db6220c1fddc9e9c","tid":1023556,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾股"},{"pid":"5dafa0927f760aff97b49cc4a8493a6a48b0ecb1","tid":1023556,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fac06b53b636bdb55c98aeb5b99450cec649ab6","tid":1023556,"uid":123559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:20:54.000Z","msg":"比亞迪 we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T06:03:39.000Z","msg":"連查理芒格都睇好，tesla準備執笠都得了<img src=\"